---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Offerings | Chaos With Clarity" description="Work with Abby: Soul + Strategy 1:1 sessions, Chaos Circles group work, and Letters from the Edge poetry collection. For founders who are financially sharp but emotionally lost.">

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <section style="padding:10rem 3rem 5rem;background:#e8dcc8;border-bottom:1px solid #cec5ad;">
    <div style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;">
      <p style="font-size:0.63rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5d6b45;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-weight:400;">Work with AJ</p>
      <h1 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(3.5rem,8vw,7rem);font-weight:600;color:#1a1612;letter-spacing:-0.02em;line-height:0.9;">Offerings</h1>
      <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.92rem;line-height:1.9;max-width:40rem;margin-top:1.75rem;">
        The CFO who can read your runway, and the poet who can sit with what the runway is actually for.
        Three ways to go deeper.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 01 SOUL + STRATEGY -->
  <section style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;padding:5.5rem 3rem;">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:3fr 2fr;gap:4rem;align-items:start;" class="offering-grid">
      <div>
        <p style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(3.5rem,7vw,6rem);color:#e0d4c0;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:1.5rem;line-height:1;letter-spacing:-0.02em;">01</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3.5vw,2.8rem);color:#1a1612;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:1.5rem;line-height:1.2;letter-spacing:0.01em;">Soul + Strategy</h2>
        <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.95rem;line-height:2.1;margin-bottom:2rem;max-width:36rem;">
          For founders who are financially sharp but emotionally lost. You've built something real — the numbers are there, or close enough. But something inside is off. You're asking questions no spreadsheet can answer: <em>What are we actually optimising for? What's the cost of a life that looks successful but feels empty?</em> This isn't coaching. This isn't therapy. It's a mirror. 90 minutes to see what's actually going on.
        </p>
        <ul style="list-style:none;margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
          <li style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#7a7260;padding:0.6rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #cec5ad;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.75rem;"><span style="color:#c17f3a;font-size:1rem;">—</span> Finance + inner pattern work</li>
          <li style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#7a7260;padding:0.6rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #cec5ad;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.75rem;"><span style="color:#c17f3a;font-size:1rem;">—</span> Lifestyle design that actually fits you</li>
          <li style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#7a7260;padding:0.6rem 0;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.75rem;"><span style="color:#c17f3a;font-size:1rem;">—</span> One-on-one, held with full presence</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://calendly.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="display:inline-block;background:#c17f3a;color:#f3e8d8;font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:0.95rem 2.2rem;text-decoration:none;font-weight:400;">Book a Call</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#e8dcc8;border:1px solid #cec5ad;padding:2.5rem;position:sticky;top:8rem;">
        <p style="font-size:0.63rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5d6b45;margin-bottom:1rem;font-weight:400;">Investment</p>
        <p style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem);color:#c17f3a;font-weight:600;line-height:1;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">₹15,000</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#7a7260;margin-bottom:2rem;">Single session · 90 minutes</p>
        <div style="border-top:1px solid #cec5ad;padding-top:1.5rem;">
          <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#7a7260;line-height:1.9;">Includes pre-session reflection, the 90-minute call, and a written summary of what surfaced.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;padding:0 3rem;"><div style="height:1px;background:#cec5ad;"></div></div>

  <!-- 02 + 03 side by side -->
  <section style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;padding:5.5rem 3rem;">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:0;border:1px solid #cec5ad;" class="pair-grid">

      <!-- 02 Chaos Circles -->
      <div style="padding:3rem;border-right:1px solid #cec5ad;">
        <p style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:3rem;color:#ddd5be;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:1.25rem;line-height:1;letter-spacing:-0.02em;">02</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.7rem;color:#1a1612;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.2;letter-spacing:0.01em;">Chaos Circles</h2>
        <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.88rem;line-height:2;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Six people who are done pretending everything is fine. Six weeks of poems, questions, and the kind of honesty that only happens in small rooms. No fixing. Just witnessing.</p>
        <ul style="list-style:none;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
          <li style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#7a7260;padding:0.4rem 0;display:flex;gap:0.6rem;"><span style="color:#5d6b45;">—</span> Intimate small group</li>
          <li style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#7a7260;padding:0.4rem 0;display:flex;gap:0.6rem;"><span style="color:#5d6b45;">—</span> A container for real things</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#1a1612;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-weight:400;">Next circle: <strong>March 2026</strong></p>
        <a href="https://typeform.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="display:inline-block;font-size:0.63rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5d6b45;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid #5d6b45;padding:0.65rem 1.25rem;font-weight:400;">Join Waitlist</a>
      </div>

      <!-- 03 Letters from the Edge -->
      <div style="padding:3rem;">
        <p style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:3rem;color:#ddd5be;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:1.25rem;line-height:1;letter-spacing:-0.02em;">03</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.7rem;color:#1a1612;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.2;letter-spacing:0.01em;">Letters from the Edge</h2>
        <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.88rem;line-height:2;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">A curated collection of poems from three years of writing — on money, mortality, love, and the strange gift of being alive. Something to return to when the noise gets loud.</p>
        <ul style="list-style:none;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
          <li style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#7a7260;padding:0.4rem 0;display:flex;gap:0.6rem;"><span style="color:#c17f3a;">—</span> Designed for slow, repeated reading</li>
          <li style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#7a7260;padding:0.4rem 0;display:flex;gap:0.6rem;"><span style="color:#c17f3a;">—</span> Your pocket poet for uncertain days</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://stripe.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="display:inline-block;background:#c17f3a;color:#f3e8d8;font-size:0.63rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:0.75rem 1.6rem;text-decoration:none;font-weight:400;">Buy Now</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PULL QUOTE + CTA -->
  <section style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;padding:0 3rem 7rem;text-align:center;">
    <div style="border-top:1px solid #cec5ad;padding-top:4rem;">
      <p style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(1.3rem,3vw,2rem);color:#1a1612;font-style:italic;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">"Abby's poems land like quiet thunder."</p>
      <p style="font-size:0.7rem;color:#7a7260;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:3.5rem;">— A reader</p>
      <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:#7a7260;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Not sure which is right for you?</p>
      <a href="/about" style="display:inline-block;font-size:0.66rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#7a7260;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid #cec5ad;padding:0.75rem 1.75rem;font-weight:400;">Read About Abby →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .offering-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
    .pair-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
    .pair-grid > div:first-child { border-right: none !important; border-bottom: 1px solid #cec5ad; }
  }
</style>
